WEBVTT

47:05.734 --> 47:08.900
I believe that If he gets married
again, everything will be alright.

47:10.692 --> 47:12.567
What type of girl are
you expecting for him?

47:12.650 --> 47:14.192
I can also help you in finding her.

47:14.567 --> 47:15.275
Viji...

47:15.817 --> 47:17.192
Why don't you marry him?

47:18.234 --> 47:19.859
Uncle, I am married.

47:20.609 --> 47:21.650
But separated.

47:24.234 --> 47:25.150
Did my father tell you?

47:26.400 --> 47:27.484
Kumaran told me.
